{"id":44846,"title":"機動武鬥傳G鋼彈","category":["機戰","科幻"],"premiere":[1994,4,1],"ep":49,"author":"富野由悠季／矢立肇","website":"","description":"在未來世紀（Future Century，F.C.）由於地球嚴重被污染，人類移往宇宙殖民星，建立了新香港、新中國、新日本、新美國等殖民星國。各國在地球雖然還存有領土，但已受到嚴重忽視。\n\n為避免戰爭，各國決定以一場鋼彈擂臺賽──鋼彈武鬥（Gundam Fight）來決定各殖民星國對地球的統治權。比賽每四年一度，以地球為擂台，每個國家（殖民星）派出一位代表參賽，一對一以鋼彈對戰，直至只有一名勝利者。勝利者所屬國家可獲得各殖民星國及地球管理權四年，直至另一個國家在下一次鋼彈對決獲勝。","image":"https://myself-bbs.com/data/attachment/forum/202302/12/200330mjln8vltgnzl1gmp.jpg","episodes":{"第 01 話":"AgADwAgAAi-xOVc","第 02 話":"AgADwQgAAi-xOVc","第 03 話":"AgADwggAAi-xOVc","第 04 話":"AgADwwgAAi-xOVc","第 05 話":"AgADxAgAAi-xOVc","第 06 話":"AgADxQgAAi-xOVc","第 07 話":"AgADxwgAAi-xOVc","第 08 話":"AgADyAgAAi-xOVc","第 09 話":"AgADyggAAi-xOVc","第 10 話":"AgADywgAAi-xOVc","第 11 話":"AgADzggAAi-xOVc","第 12 話":"AgAD0AgAAi-xOVc","第 13 話":"AgAD0QgAAi-xOVc","第 14 話":"AgAD0ggAAi-xOVc","第 15 話":"AgAD1AgAAi-xOVc","第 16 話":"AgAD1ggAAi-xOVc","第 17 話":"AgAD1wgAAi-xOVc","第 18 話":"AgAD2AgAAi-xOVc","第 19 話":"AgAD2QgAAi-xOVc","第 20 話":"AgAD2ggAAi-xOVc","第 21 話":"AgAD1wcAAt5NSFc","第 22 話":"AgAD2AcAAt5NSFc","第 23 話":"AgAD2QcAAt5NSFc","第 24 話":"AgAD2gcAAt5NSFc","第 25 話":"AgAD2wcAAt5NSFc","第 26 話":"AgAD3AcAAt5NSFc","第 27 話":"AgAD3QcAAt5NSFc","第 28 話":"AgAD3wcAAt5NSFc","第 29 話":"AgAD4AcAAt5NSFc","第 30 話":"AgAD4QcAAt5NSFc","第 31 話":"AgAD4gcAAt5NSFc","第 32 話":"AgAD5AcAAt5NSFc","第 33 話":"AgAD5gcAAt5NSFc","第 34 話":"AgAD6QcAAt5NSFc","第 35 話":"AgAD6gcAAt5NSFc","第 36 話":"AgAD7QcAAt5NSFc","第 37 話":"AgAD7gcAAt5NSFc","第 38 話":"AgAD8AcAAt5NSFc","第 39 話":"AgAD8gcAAt5NSFc","第 40 話":"AgAD-gcAAt5NSFc","第 41 話":"AgADEggAAt5NSFc","第 42 話":"AgADFAgAAt5NSFc","第 43 話":"AgADFQgAAt5NSFc","第 44 話":"AgADFwgAAt5NSFc","第 45 話":"AgADGAgAAt5NSFc","第 46 話":"AgADGQgAAt5NSFc","第 47 話":"AgADGggAAt5NSFc","第 48 話":"AgADGwgAAt5NSFc","第 49 話":"AgADHAgAAt5NSFc"}}